<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFF2FFECE0F802D5FCD3FD6A" author="Korb, S. K. &amp; Stradomsky, B. V. &amp; Kuznetsov, G." box="[450,880,654,681]" pageId="10" pageNumber="35" pagination="140 - 145" refId="ref9752" refString="Korb, S. K., Stradomsky, B. V. &amp; Kuznetsov, G. (2015) Two new subspecies of Melitaea ornata Christoph, 1893 (Lepidoptera, Nymphalidae) from Europe and Middle Asia. Amurian zoological journal, VII (2), 140 - 145." type="journal article" year="2015">Korb, Stradomsky &amp; Kuznetsov, 2015</bibRefCitation>
